author: dims
msg: - Fixed BeanDeserializer to use the propertyMap instead of the array.
- Fixed RPCElement to set elementIsFirstParam=true for the STYLE_WRAPPED style.
- Fixed SymbolTable to generate correct code for "wrapped" request.
- Add "wrapped" sample to test the code and make sure it does not break in the future.

author: gdaniels
msg: Fix for fault code equality check,  submitted by Adam Leggett.
Also remove print of configPath, which is a small but real security
hole (gives away absolute paths on server).

author: butek
msg: Make sure escaped characters in the WSDL  address stay escaped in the Java string.

author: gdaniels
msg: Add static accessor to centralize access to type metadata for a class.
For now this is limited to using the static getTypeDesc() method if it is
found, but will allow us to add file-based metadata descriptors later.
